what is wifi, wifi is a technology to transfer information over radio signals. wifi is a standard and a trademark meaning IEEE 802.11x, and it is owend by WI-FI Alliance, the deffination of wifi is wireless local area network (WLAN). Your computer or mobile device need a wifi sender and reaciver to use wifi. the wifi works by creating an electromagnetic field, in the spectrum 2.4 and 5.0 GHz, which is the standard given by the wifi Alliance. wifi can be used to calgulate the position of a person or a piece of hardwdare.